      <title>石油交易商预计 OPEC+ 维持当前供应限制的可能性为 70%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/oil-traders-see-70-chance-of-opec-holding-current-supply-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据芝加哥商品交易所集团 (CME Group) 的期权持仓情况，石油交易员认为 OPEC+ 在本周末会议上不改变当前减产措施的可能性约为 70%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/oil-traders-see-70-chance-of-opec-holding-current-supply-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 部长前往利雅得，会议地点再次变更</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/opec-changes-meeting-venue-again-as-ministers-head-to-riyadh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据代表们透露，OPEC+ 将第二次更改 6 月会议地点，部长们目前计划在利雅得亲自讨论石油政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/opec-changes-meeting-venue-again-as-ministers-head-to-riyadh</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:17:52 GMT</pubDate>
