      <title>激进主义者呼吁出售赌场公司后，宾夕法尼亚大学股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/penn-shares-soar-after-activist-calls-for-sale-of-casino-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名激进投资者呼吁出售这家赌场公司，并称交易失败和越来越多的未达到预期目标已经损害了管理层的信誉，此后，宾夕法尼亚娱乐公司 (Penn Entertainment Inc.) 的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/penn-shares-soar-after-activist-calls-for-sale-of-casino-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 14:47:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Oppenheimer 的 Stoltzfus 表示，标普指数年底前可能突破 5,500 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/oppenheimer-s-stoltzfus-says-s-p-could-top-5-500-by-year-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Oppenheimer 的 John Stoltzfus 表示，标准普尔 500 指数年底前可能突破 5,500 点。他表示，盈利情况强劲，美国消费者仍在消费。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/oppenheimer-s-stoltzfus-says-s-p-could-top-5-500-by-year-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 14:34:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀指标支撑美联储降息前景，债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/treasury-yields-dip-after-inflation-gauges-match-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券周五上涨，延续月度涨幅，此前温和的通胀数据维持了人们对美联储今年将至少降息一次的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/treasury-yields-dip-after-inflation-gauges-match-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
